dlentry.dd:
Changes the style of the selected text tobold by surrounding it with
            hi tag and setting the rend attribute to
            bold;

Changes the style of the selected text toitalic by surrounding it with
            hi tag and setting the rend attribute to
            italic;

Changes the style of the selected text tounderline by surrounding it with hi tag and setting the rend attribute to ul;
Bold, Italic, and Underline are toggle actions.
For all of the above actions, if there is no selection, then a new specific tag will be inserted. These actions are available in any document context.

Inserts a new section / subsection, depending on the current context. For example if the
          current context isdiv1 then a div2 will be inserted and
          so on;
